<title>Mission</title>

<para>
    The <command>centos-art.sh</command> script exists to automate
    frequent tasks inside &TCAR;.  The
    <command>centos-art.sh</command> script is organized in
    independent functions which try to follow the paradigm of doing
    just one thing and do it well.
</para>
